						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">mattdc wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Was hoping for some support in compiling Nesicide2 for OSX 10.5x.  I'm not sure where to start.  I downloaded the tar file from the GIT repository, created a new directory, dropped the tar in and thats where I am now.  any help would be appreciated.</div>
